Originally ripped by Terminal Escape, posted on July 12, 2015 Description from Terminal Escape:
I know that all of you punks have scooped the RIXE single by now (and if you haven't, then you should), but there's another French Oi! band, slightly more under-the-radar, that you need to get hip to. You can thank me after you listen to this shit. TRAITRE
